
Basic Build
------------------

It can be built with pure make (last resort), cmake, or meson (preferable)

1) make
make
#sudo make install

2) cmake
cmake -B _build -S $(pwd)
cmake --build _build
#sudo cmake --install _build

2) meson
meson setup _build
meson compile -C _build
#sudo meson install -C _build


Package Templates
------------------

Templates are located in
debian/
rpmlinux/
archlinux/
snap/

